### Highest Annual Earnings

This section is a bit of a moving target, a snapshot of who ruled the roost in any given year. [Forbes](/Forbes) compiles these lists, and while they’re based on earnings from June to June, they give a pretty clear picture of who’s at the top of the food chain. Remember, these figures often include more than just acting salaries – endorsements, production deals, the whole package.

**Dwayne Johnson** has been a consistent presence, topping the list multiple times (2016, 2019, 2020, 2021, and 2024). He’s a machine, both on and off screen. **Julia Roberts** was the reigning queen for a stretch in the late 90s and early 2000s.

